o purchase back the preferred stock and in march  exercised this right paying  billion to berkshire the preferred stock could only be purchased back at a  premium the warrants have been exercised and berkshire holds  of the share capital of goldman sachs profit on the preferred stock was estimated at  billion and exercising the warrants has yielded a profit of more than  billion berkshire still owns shares in goldman sachs so the entire profit cannot be quantified on august   berkshire hathaway purchased  billion of preferred shares in bank of america the investment has an annual interest cost of  earning berkshire  million in annual interest alongside the preferred stock investment berkshire obtained warrants allowing berkshire to buy  million common shares at  per share any time before september   based on the share price in june  this position has yielded a profit of more than  billion excluding the annual interest earned from the preferred stock vandergriff automotive the highest selling honda dealership in the dallas metroplex contributes  million in revenue every year in  pepsi paid berkshire  million to insure against a contest pepsi held which had a potential  billion prize the prize had a very small chance of being won and it was not won by anyone in  berkshire hathaway inc acquired russell corporation for  million in fact getting most shares and brands in many sports leagues – including spalding nba official basketballs bike athletic company protections aai american athletic gymnastics tables bars rings horses or dudley softball balls and accessories in  berkshire purchased preferred stock in wrigley goldman sachs and ge totaling  billion on november   berkshire hathaway announced that using stock and cash totaling  billion it would acquire the remaining  percent of the burlington northern santa fe corporation parent of bnsf railway that it did not already own this was the largest acquisition todate in berkshires history on march   berkshire hathaway annou