er term profitability could be achieved in an industry that has historically been loss making in aggregate prior investmentsedit berkshire previously held a considerable stake in tesco plc the uk grocery retailer berkshire made its first investment in tesco in  and in  raised this stake to over  of the company with a cost for the investment of  billion buffett sold around  of this stake in  when he “soured somewhat on the company’s thenmanagement” realising a profit of  million as tescos problems mounted through  berkshire sold all the remaining shares with buffett saying to shareholders that the delay in selling shares was costly berkshire made an aftertax loss of  million on the tesco investment subsidiaries and equity holdingsedit main article list of assets owned by berkshire hathaway assetsedit main article list of assets owned by berkshire hathaway see alsoedit nebraska portal companies portal list of berkshire hathaway publications notesedit  a b c d e f berkshire hathaway inc  annual report form k xbrl united states securities and exchange commission february     berkshire hathaway portfolio tracker cnbc retrieved    warren buffett  annual report pdf p  retrieved  may    top  biggest conglomerates in the world based by revenue therichest  retrieved    the worlds biggest public companies forbescom retrieved may     berkshire hathaway forbes retrieved june     fuhrmann ryan  may  whats the most expensive stock of all time investopedia   providence journal article july   projocom july   retrieved on july    seabury stanton – – find a grave memorial findagravecom november   retrieved may     a b buffetts worst trade cnbc february   retrieved on july    friedman nicole june   berkshire unit settles with california regulator over workers comp insurance wall street journal new york city united states retrieved june     berkshire hathaway to join sp  shares soar reuters january   retrieved january     yousuf hibah february   buffetts berkshire hathaway joins sp  ind